{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"9e2fb5f1bc38cbd8","x":-1160,"y":-30,"width":1660,"height":350,"type":"text","text":"```mermaid\nclassDiagram\n    direction LR\n\n    class Player {\n        +RuneBuffer: Map<RuneType, Count>\n        +ConsumeRune(rune): Boolean\n        +CheckForSpell(): Spell\n    }\n\n    class SpellResolver {\n        -Ruleset: List<Rule>\n        +ResolveBaseSpell(sequence): BaseSpell\n        +ApplyModifiers(baseSpell, remainingRunes): FinalSpell\n    }\n\n    class Rule {\n        +Priority: Integer\n        +Name: String\n        +ValidSequence: SequencePattern\n    }\n\n    class Spell {\n        <<Abstract>>\n        +BaseType: Enum (Internal/Projected/Special)\n        +CastingLogic(): void\n    }\n\n    class BaseSpell {\n        +Name: String\n        +RequiredRunes: List<Rune>\n    }\n\n    class Modifier {\n        +Effect: String (e.g., Piercing, Burning)\n        +AppliesTo: SpellType\n    }\n\n    class Rune {\n        <<Component>>\n        +Element: Enum (Fire/Wind/Earth/Lightning)\n        +KeyBinding: Char\n    }\n\n    Player --> \"*\" Rune : uses >\n    Player --> SpellResolver : feeds sequence to >\n    SpellResolver --> Rule : scans against >\n    Rule \"1\" --o BaseSpell : identifies >\n    BaseSpell *-- \"*\" Modifier : can accept >\n    Modifier ..> Spell : modifies >\n    Rune <|-- ElementRune : inherits (Q, W, E, R)\n    Rune <|-- CoreRune : inherits (A, S, D)\n\n```"}
